<section class="markdown" data-translation="true">
## Receiving the return value

Now, add the following code to the end of view.phtml.

```php
&lt;?php return 'Romance dawn!' ?&gt;
```

In `index.php`, modify it as follows:

```php
//  Create an argument.
$args = [
    'p' => 'The NEW WORLD is a new world.',
];

//  Pass it as the second argument and receive the return value
$return = OP()->Template('view.phtml', $args);
D( $return );
```

Reload the page in your browser to see if the changes are reflected.
</section>

